ments/DOC-400895A1.pdf">FCC chair Jessica Rosenworcel warns</a> will cause some to lose access altogether.</p><br/></div></div></div><div class="duet--content-cards--content-card relative flex flex-row border-b border-solid border-gray-cc px-0 last-of-type:border-b-0 dark:border-gray-31 py-16 hover:bg-[#FBF9FF] dark:hover:bg-gray-18 max-w-container-md last-of-type:border-b-0 md:pl-20"><a class="hover:shadow-underline-inherit after:absolute after:inset-0" aria-label="Play Store developers can link to outside payment offers in the EU this week." href="/2024/3/5/24090685/play-store-developers-can-link-to-outside-payment-offers-in-the-eu-this-week"></a><div class="w-38 relative flex min-w-[38px] flex-col md:ml-[-3px] md:items-start"><div class="absolute ml-0 w-24"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 134.51 284.18" width="24" height="50" class="h-50 w-24"><defs><linearGradient id="gradient25" gradientTransform="rotate(90)"><stop offset="40%" stop-color="#3CFFD0"></stop><stop offset="55%" stop-color="#5200FF"></stop></linearGradient></defs><g id="Layer_2" data-name="Layer 2"><g id="Layer_1-2" data-name="Layer 1"><path fill="url(#gradient25)" class="cls-1" d="M110.91,165.78h0c-18-15.39-18-32,0-47.39h0a67.26,67.26,0,1,0-87.31,0h0c18,15.39,18,32,0,47.39h0a67.26,67.26,0,1,0,87.31,0Z"></path></g></g></svg></div><div class="z-10 flex h-24 w-24 justify-center px-4 py-6 text-center font-polysans text-11 font-bold leading-none tracking-normal text-black">A</div><div class="z-10 mt-2 flex h-24 w-24 justify-center p-[5px] text-center text-black"><span class="flex w-full justify-center"><svg class="" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 11 11" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>External Link</title><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M6.8999 0.400024H10.8999V4.40002H9.8999V2.10713L4.8999 7.10713L4.1928 6.40002L9.1928 1.40002H6.8999V0.400024ZM2.3999 2.90002C2.12604 2.90002 1.8999 3.12617 1.8999 3.40002V8.90002C1.8999 9.03263 1.95258 9.15